### Register (Manager)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Manager",
  "email": "manager@test.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "MANAGER"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "manager@test.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Health check
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

###
# Copy the token from the login response and paste it below (replace YOUR_TOKEN_HERE)
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Create order template (Manager only)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/orders/templates
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Open the store",
  "dayOfWeek": 1,
  "category": "daily"
}

### Sync / run rollover
POST http://localhost:3000/api/orders/sync
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get orders for today
GET http://localhost:3000/api/orders?startDate=2026-03-28&endDate=2026-03-28
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Toggle instance (replace 1 with a real id from the GET response)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/orders/instances/1/toggle
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
